OL,3,CReeves to cut electricity bills for
OL,4,Cthousands more UK manufacturers
OL,6,FThe government has widened its plans
OL,7,Fto reduce electricity costs for
OL,8,Fthousands of UK manufacturers as the
OL,9,Fconflict in the Middle East continues
OL,10,Fto drive up energy prices.
OL,12,FChancellor Rachel Reeves announced the
OL,13,Fmeasures after warning that the
OL,14,Flingering impact of the Iran war could
OL,15,Fweigh on inflation and economic growth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
