OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776345056
OL,3,CReeves to cut electricity bills for
OL,4,Cthousands more UK manufacturers
OL,6,FSpeaking from Washington where she is
OL,7,Fattending the International Monetary
OL,8,FFund (IMF) spring meetings, Reeves
OL,9,Fsaid the plan will help British
OL,10,Fbusinesses remain competitive and
OL,11,Fcreate jobs despite the uncertain
OL,12,Feconomic outlook.
OL,14,FLast summer, the government announced
OL,15,Fa plan to cut electricity bills by up
OL,16,Fto 25% for more than 7,000 UK
OL,17,Fbusinesses, as part of a 10-year
OL,18,Findustrial strategy.
OL,20,FOn Wednesday, it revealed plans to
OL,21,Fexpand this to cover 10,000 firms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
