OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776345056
OL,3,CReeves to cut electricity bills for
OL,4,Cthousands more UK manufacturers
OL,6,FThe British Industrial Competitiveness
OL,7,FScheme (BICS) will cut costs by up to
OL,8,F#40 per megawatt-hour from 2027 by
OL,9,Fexempting businesses from certain
OL,10,Fextra charges that currently support
OL,11,Fgreen energy and back-up power supply
OL,12,Fsystems.
OL,14,FIt said it plans to roll out an
OL,15,Fadditional one-off payment in 2027 to
OL,16,Fan additional 3,000 businesses,
OL,17,Fincluding companies in the automotive
OL,18,Fand aerospace, steel, and
OL,19,Fpharmaceutical sectors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
