PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1776345056
OL,3,CReeves to cut electricity bills for
OL,4,Cthousands more UK manufacturers
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe government said it will also cover
OL,12,Fthe support firms would have received
OL,13,Fif the BICS had been in place from
OL,14,Fthis month.
OL,16,FThe BICS scheme is expected to be
OL,17,Fworth up to #600 million per year from
OL,18,Fnext April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
