OL,3,CReeves to cut electricity bills for
OL,4,Cthousands more UK manufacturers
OL,6,FReeves said: "This government has the
OL,7,Fright plan for the economy: backing
OL,8,FBritish industry, cutting electricity
OL,9,Fcosts, and building a stronger, more
OL,10,Fresilient future."
OL,12,FBusiness Secretary Peter Kyle said:
OL,13,F"We are a government of action, and
OL,14,Fwhen global instability puts
OL,15,Fbusinesses under pressure we'll always
OL,16,Fdo what's needed to support them and
OL,17,Fensure Britain's resilience.
