OL,3,CReeves to cut electricity bills for
OL,4,Cthousands more UK manufacturers
OL,6,F"By extending the reach of BICS by
OL,7,F40%, we're acting decisively to tackle
OL,8,Fthe number one issue that businesses
OL,9,Fface head-on."
